# Entire assets tree (root or under version folders, e.g. v0.103.2/assets/)
assets/

# Sample / placeholder cards (root or under version folders)
**/cards/_samples/

# Any card file with "deprecated" in the name (any folder depth)
**/*deprecated*
**/*DEPRECATED*

# Mad Science colorless cards (base + upgraded)
**/cards/colorless/Mad-Science*
**/cards/colorless/*MAD_SCIENCE*
